sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { ProfileContainer, UserContainer, UserAvatar, UserName, UserTag, UserLocation, UserStats, UserStatsLi, } from './Profile.styled'; export const Profile = props => { const { username, tag, location, avatar, stats } = props; return ( {username} {tag} {location} Followers {stats.followers} Views {stats.views} Likes {stats.likes} ); };
